Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time I see him, I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you my stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me to give you my stamp,\NI'll have to take responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.63,0:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will also be joining Rin-san in\Nsupervising your behavior from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, he's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.67,0:00:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my cochon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need two people watching him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, you can just quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How unsightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost like I've run away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is that has made me go so insane...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain I felt that day\Nhas endlessly plagued me ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps my heart and body were weakened\Nby that unfamiliar damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My chest aches uncontrollably in its desire for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nomura is not a man who will submit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.96,0:01:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just the same as I.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.63,0:01:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I must continue until I reach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.33,0:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If he will not be mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,then I must kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.08,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(910,900)\blur1.5\pos(535.8,889.2)\}Episode 12
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:12.08,Ep Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(950,900)\blur1.5\pos(1350.9,889.2)\fscx80}The Girls' Machiavellism
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.58,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you said it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come at me just like a beast would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.88,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I'm doin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Jigen School's sword movements\Nare swift, as is its footwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and if the wielder's speed is raised to\Nthat of a flash of lightning, of unyou,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they tread into the territory of invisibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.96,0:03:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But his is imperfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After two or three displays,\Nthe effect loses its effectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He purposefully exposed his vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems she is more resistant to\Npiercing bare skin than clothed skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so that technique may work quite well with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were empty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew you still had your "magic bullet".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She took the magic bullet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I ain't gonna go down\Njust with one hit, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done hitting you yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a special treat,\Nso you come at me with all you got, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.79,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The last one poisoning our academy\Nof coexistence was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.25,0:06:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unexpected, but good that it was not Tsukuyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.80,0:06:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I'll show my face for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, we'll have to think of how to punish those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A student's duty, first and foremost, is to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the point of those two\Nhitting one another without defending at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts to try and understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.08,0:06:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of all, why do they seem so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be what friendship is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted this for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.92,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a pain that would help me forget\Nthe burning in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,More! Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look only at me, touch only me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,think only of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.58,0:07:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.19,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(967.999,533)\b1\bord4.5\blur4.5}Magic Bullet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.31,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(918,707)\bord4.5\blur4.5}Auto-Counter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really were holding back\Non your auto-counter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I simply wanted to do things your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it your all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.29,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too early to be exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to fire it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like overwhelming victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.13,0:08:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You calmly see your way to a chance of winning,\Nwhile purposefully taking your opponent's attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.46,0:08:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't say it's a hobby of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...to one-sidedly force someone into submission\Nand get them to listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you fight not to win, but to show where you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.25,0:08:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling that for the first time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the victor has already been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Loving is losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Amou, can we st-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes, that means absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not allow a half-hearted attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell, Nomura,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,what this ringing in my chest is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved you so strongly I wanted to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end, Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me outta that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.38,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me finish our fight as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, it does not seem as if you and I will be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I am disappointed at\Nthe crude use of your iliopsoas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And in a simple punching match,\Nyou have the physical advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.75,0:10:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But that unsightly display was proof that you have\Nnot mastered the use of your center of balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,On no account could I abandon someone\Nlearned in the same school of swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it briefly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I will become your teacher and correct you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, just before you were going on about how\NI'd caused someone trouble and you were super mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not going to let that slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, I said the patience of the Buddha has its limit,\Nup to three strikes, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be using that interpretation here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You do not want to make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it benefits us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Obedient students will naturally earn leniency.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you want this from me, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The carrot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He has to accept her offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The stamp he wanted so badly\Nhas fallen right into his lap!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a bad deal for Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Inaba doesn't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Nomura's not the kind of man\Nto nod his head in this situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I refu-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten... sou... metsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Masked girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Satori's girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.04,0:11:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukino has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On school grounds, call me by my title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.75,0:12:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the school headmaster, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.58,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sou...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Metsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, disperse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well, except for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're expelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that weird?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not after I went and did all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a guy who hates being forced into things,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,it's weird that you're just accepting it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm used to that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the help you gave me, I went and wasted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, I won't get woken up early\Nby Onigawara's shouting anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already riding a bicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Kyo-bo's doing well at the animal hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.00,0:13:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, it looks like she'll be\Nthe first one to fully recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd come all this way to visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, not here to visit you,\Nmore just here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that rumor true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're getting too worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you better, but don't hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heard you were the one who had it the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me, Nomura, are you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.96,0:14:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I dunno what expression I should make.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It ain't something you should make\Nbased on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Put on whatever expression you feel like putting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say to that sour reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.46,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure does fit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nomura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.83,0:14:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl who tried to slice me up in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.83,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are funny, Nomura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play again sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.71,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If I feel like it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, go on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh, well, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.67,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.58,0:15:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.92,0:15:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,U-umm, Miso...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Satori!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.17,0:15:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.83,0:15:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.38,0:15:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.50,0:15:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider, school headmaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura Fudo's actions were\Nall to stop Amou's rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:15:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,they were all to preserve the peace of our academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We will guarantee you of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Expelling Nomura is a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,\NI cannot reverse Nomura's expulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Never thought you'd be waiting for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I had not heard your answer to my offer to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the offer, but you heard why\NI can't be your student, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that is disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you intend to leave this place, like the Empress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you haven't heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She gathered up her belongings\Nand has already gone to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're not allowed to leave the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't apply anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be expelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.71,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the paperwork is completed,\Nyou are still a student of this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you have a permission slip\Nstamped by all five Swords,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you are not allowed to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.25,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should hurry if you're going to\Nrun after her, my pupil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Headin' out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause I didn't think you'd leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Just came to ask why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to that I got forced into being her student.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanna run away from it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna run away with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.71,0:17:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do as I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why you should be yourself and do as you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have anything you wanna tell them,\NI can pass it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.80,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one thing I didn't get to say back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologize to them for the misinformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially to those Five Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, now, when the hell did I become yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.04,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment we met, you have always\Nbeen mine, deep within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.14,0:19:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you! Goin' on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you idiot! This is what I normally wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.54,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.33,0:19:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally got to see you in casual wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a good eye for fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,H-huh, w-well anyway, were you glad you went?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Amou, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand each other well enough now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little reluctant, but I don't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so about getting expelled...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.67,0:19:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! About that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kikakujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-san, I am exceedingly disgusted that\Nyou would try to sneak ahead of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.04,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You just took much too long to get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A-anyway! Let me explain about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,\NI cannot reverse Nomura's expulsion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-the school headmaster was joking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard her joke before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, considering your words,\NI will say that was the true circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, the two of you need to\Ntightly hold onto his reins.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So Nomura, you can stay at the Acad...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nomura Fudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the other men, you must choose\Nto either coexist with us here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or leave this academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Make your choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all here, might as well have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to have you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.33,0:22:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The view from the outside is pretty great!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not half bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Aichi Coexistence Academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.00,0:22:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My beautiful alma mater!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
